title: Harvick dominates in must-win race to advance in Chase
text:
> Pennsylvania Harvick dominates in must-win race to advance in Chase Kevin Harvick places his nameplate on the Chase Grid in Victory Lane after he won the NASCAR Sprint Cup series auto race, Sunday, Oct. 4, 2015, at Dover International Speedway in Dover, Del.
